The unit is within minutes of Melbourne Airport and just 1.5km* of the Western Ring Road interchange off Airport Drive, providing excellent access to all major road arterial.

+ Total building area: 528sqm*
+ Two-level corporate office: 394sqm*
+ High clearance warehouse area: 134sqm*
+ One (1) container height roller shutter door

+ Open plan and partitioned office areas on both levels
+ Full amenities including kitchenette and male & female bathrooms
+ 10kva solar unit
+ 2 x Separate aircon units on Ground Floor and Mezzanine
+ 7 car spaces
+ Three (3) Phase power

Please contact the marketing agents for inspection and further information.
